  "title": "Wooden Tool Variants",
  "description": "A Mod that adds Wooden Tools for each wood type. Fabric and Forge compatible",
  "body": "<center>\n\n<div><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/Imgs/logo.png\" width=\"625\" height=\"195\" /></div>\n    \n</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/Imgs/strip.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<h3>This mod adds wooden tools for each wood type!</h3>\n\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Spruce</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/spruce_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td><td>Birch</td>\n\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/birch_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td><td>Jungle</td>\n\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/jungle_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td><td>Acacia</td>\n\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/acacia_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td><td>Dark Oak</td>\n\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/dark_oak_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td></tr>\n<tr>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\n<td>Mangrove</td>\n\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/mangrove_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td>\n\n<td>Cherry</td><td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/cherry_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td>\n\n<td>Bamboo</td><td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/bamboo_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td>\n\n<td>Crimson</td><td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/crimson_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td>\n\n<td>Warped</td>\n\n<td><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/src/main/resources/assets/woodentoolvariants/textures/item/warped_pickaxe.png\" width=\"60\" style=\"image-rendering: pixelated;\"></td></tr>\n\n<tr></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>A great complementary mod for <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/more-crafting-tables-for-forge\">More Crafting Tables</a> and <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/more-chest-variants-lieonlion\">More Chest Variants</a></h4>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/quad\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/Quad/main/requireQuad.png\" width=\"190\"/></a></h3>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1/fabric/Imgs/strip.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/SniffBakaSniff/Wooden-Tool-Variants-1.20.1\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=ff0000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"130\" style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" />\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@Subaka_\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=ff0000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"135\" style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" />\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/wooden-tool-variants\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=ff0000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"162\" style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" />\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/.subaka/mods\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=ff0000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"148\" style=\"color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none;\" />\n</a>\n\n\n    \n</center>\n\n",
